Connect to ssh running on port 44.

Download the bootstrap.tar from https://cameronkatri.com/bootstrap-ssh.tar.zst and unzst it, then upload it to your device.

Extract it to /private/preboot/ACTIVE
symlink it to /var/jb ( ln -s /private/preboot/ACTIVE/var/jb /var/jb )
symlink /var/jb to /var/jb/var/jb ( ln -s /var/jb /var/jb/var/jb )
Execute /var/jb/prep_bootstrap.sh, then run /var/jb/usr/bin/login and login as mobile.
Once logged in as mobile, run sudo passwd and set a root password, then login as root.

To install ElleKit rootless:

curl -sLO https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1028398976640229380/1055561517359181894/ellekit_rootless.deb
dpkg --force-all -i ellekit_rootless.deb
rm -rf /var/jb/usr/lib/ellekit/pspawn.dylib
curl -sL https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1028398976640229380/1055565626002911253/pspawn.dylib --output /var/jb/usr/lib/ellekit/pspawn.dylib
ln -s /private/preboot/$(cat /private/preboot/active)/var/jb/usr/lib/libsubstitute.dylib /private/preboot/$(cat /private/preboot/active)/var/jb/Library/Frameworks/CydiaSubstrate.framework/CydiaSubstrate

Now you can install any tweak using dpkg, if you want Sileo you'll need to install the rootless deb from Pogo or something. Be sure to REBOOT or USERSPACE REBOOT after installing any tweaks, because ellekit needs that.

Enjoy!
